GLOBALDATA DIVISION.
PIC9 X VALUE 0.
PIC9 Y.

PROGRAM DIVISION.

MAISUM PIC9 USING PIC9 ARG1.

PERFORM UNTIL (ARG1 < 1000).
DISPLAY ARG1.
ACCEPT ARG1 FROM COMPUTE(ARG1 + 1).
ENDPERFORM
RETURN ARG1.

ENDFUNCTION



MAISUMCONT PIC9 USING PIC9 ARG1.
	PERFORM UNTIL (ARG1 < 1000).

		DISPLAY ARG1.

			IF (ARG1=346) THEN
			DISPLAY 9999999.
			RETURN ARG1.
			ENDIF

		ACCEPT ARG1 FROM COMPUTE(ARG1 + 3).

	ENDPERFORM
ENDFUNCTION



MAIN.
PIC9 ARG1 VALUE 0.
PICBOOL VDD VALUE TRUE.
ACCEPT Y FROM CALL MAISUMCONT USING ARG1..
DISPLAY Y.
ENDMAIN

